<plot>Every morning the sun comes up and Steve and Dean meet on a bench to drink beer and discuss life while the world passes them by, literally. Steve is waiting for a catalyst to bring an arc into his life, to propel him back into the arms of his wife. What could a crazy guy who shows up every morning at 9:21 possibly mean to that arc? And what will Steve and Dean do the morning Skinny Jimmy doesn't show on his appointed rounds?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?044666</url></doc>
